<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Docker-Compose - 分类 - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/docker-compose/</link><description>You got a dream, you gotta protect it.</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>zh-cn</language><managingEditor>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:23:13 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/docker-compose/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docker Compose简化复杂应用的利器</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150830-docker-compose%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E5%99%A8/</link><pubDate>Sun, 30 Aug 2015 15:59:00 +0000</pubDate><author>tom920wt@hotmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/20150830-docker-compose%E7%AE%80%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E5%99%A8/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8/">容器</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/docker-compose/">Docker-Compose</category><description>&lt;p>Docker Compose是用于定义和运行复杂Docker应用的工具。你可以在一个文件中定义一个多容器的应用，然后使用一条命令来启动你的应用，然后所有相关的操作都会被自动完成。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Docker Compose具有管理应用程序整个生命周期的命令：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>启动，停止和重建服务&lt;/li>
&lt;li>查看正在运行的服务的状态&lt;/li>
&lt;li>流式传输运行服务的日志输出&lt;/li>
&lt;li>在服务上运行一次性命令&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="docker-compose-安装" class="heading-element">&lt;span>Docker Compose 安装&lt;/span>
 &lt;a href="#docker-compose-%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85" class="heading-mark">
